android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.FOREGROUND_SERVICE.description: Allows a regular application to use Service.startForeground

android.permission.MOUNT_UNMOUNT_FILESYS.description: Allows the application to mount and unmount file systems for removable storage.

playstore_details.title: Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid
playstore_details.description:
Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid is the best photo collage layout tool!It is an easy-to-use collage photo editor and collage maker software. You can pick layout you want it to be, and Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid provides diverse amazing stickers, art filter and awesome collages to help you to create perfect picture collages.

Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid's smooth, intuitive process make it very easy to control your editing & making. It supports up to 20 photos collage and more than 100 different layouts. You can share your amazing beauty photos for Instagram or Twitter or Facebook with Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid.

Features:
100+ Layouts of frames or grids to choose from!You can pick layout you like best, edit collage with filter sticker text background and much more.
Freestyel!For each layout, you can drag and drop to adjust the layout size. That means you can create any grid for your photos.
100+ Background to choose from!Multiple backgrounds for your photo such as, black, white,blur, etc.We also designed beautiful patterns love dot texture and so on.
Add funny ptickers on photo.Add funny emoji or selfie makeup stickers on your picture.We designed lots of classical and funny stickers for your collage photos.
Coolest filter Effects.There are lots of filter Effects you can selected.You can transform daily moments into creative photos anytime.
Add text on your photo.Allow you to add text on your collaged photos. Make a happy emotion text with your beautiful picture!

If you are looking for a powerful app for photo collage, Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid is your best choice!!! And if you have any problems or suggestions, feel free to let us know. 

Pic Collage Maker- Blur Background Photo Edit Grid has everything you need to create fantastic collages with your photos. Try it!!!
